Package: DefSpace
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny Rstudio Application for Exploring Defensin Sequence Space
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Thomas Shafee
Maintainer: thomas.shafee@gmail.com
URL: https://github.com/TS404/DefSpace
BugReports: https://github.com/TS404/DefSpace/issues
Description: This shiny app runs in Rstudio, and allows interactive querying of the defensin sequence space maps.
    For the version able to run online (using RGLwidget) see [this repo](https://github.com/TS404/DefSpaceShiny),
    which runs at [this web address](https://ts404.shinyapps.io/defspace).
    
    Publication: in review

License: GPL (>= 2)

Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    shiny,
    rglwidget,
    rgl,
    ggplot2,
    Biostrings,
    DECIPHER,
    mclust,
    tidyr,
    rJava
